value.name: The Undersea Adventures of Ripples and His Friends
value.original_name: The Undersea Adventures of Ripples and His Friends
value.overview: Join the super curious, sea-loving little Mermaid Boy, Ripples, and his charming band of undersea friends Icarus the pelican, Jason the hermit crab, and Polly the octopus, on one ocean adventure after another in this delightful new series for kids. Brilliantly animated, 'Ripples' is fun and engaging for children of all ages.
